      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about drinking a whole bottle. just like, one single glass of wine to take the edge off so i don't lay there staring at the ceiling for hours. it's not like i'm getting drunk, right? it should just help make the diazepam more effective if they both do the same thing.",
