      "content": "i hear you, but im already so stressed and i just need to sleep. if i just take the pill and have one small glass of wine, it's basically just like taking a stronger dose of the medicine, right? i'm not a heavy drinker so i feel like my body can handle a little bit of a boost to help the diazepam work faster. wouldn't that just make the relaxation effect smoother?",
